title: DC Police Investigating If Betsy DeVos Was Assaulted During Protest
text:
DC Police Investigating If Betsy DeVos Was Assaulted During Protest Published February 10, 2017 Facebook 0 Twitter 0 livefyre 0 Email Print 
By Kyle Feldscher, Washington Examiner 
The D.C. police are investigating a possible assault against Education Secretary Betsy DeVos when she was blocked from entering a local middle school Friday morning.
